Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方睡觉是不行的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.71,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次睡到桌子底下去 已经是小时候的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被麻幌发现了不知道她会怎么念我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.97,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌已经睡了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那片蔚蓝的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是生命的神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以估量的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那片蔚蓝的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将圣者的心拉到这里来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的数年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因圣者的科技而诞生的我们这些战斗用机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经由合成的身体组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以工学编织而成的中枢神经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为战斗用的装置 而被制造出来的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连在这人工的心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有着被深深刻印的昔日记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的宇宙记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣者究竟前进了多远的距离？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.12,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这宇宙中究竟旁徨了多久的时间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在银河的那层面纱的更深处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在无数散布的星星之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍是旅程起点的星球 应该也还存在於某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个星球的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连圣者的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也已经没有人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一残留的只有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深蓝的记忆而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.16,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的旅程期间人们所经验的无数事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.06,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都累积于给予数十个世代指引的圣者之母“马修”之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于马修那完全的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.84,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一世代的人们出发前往宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.18,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃了培育自己生命 像是母亲般的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未曾回头的移民船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了未知的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜访无数的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处寻找与自己能够接触的文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.17,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在这浩瀚宇宙之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说是遇见文明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连任何生命的痕迹也无法找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为面临绝种的焦虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及重重失望之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次到达的生命之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个蓝色的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与这个梦想中的文明的第一次接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是偶发事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.53,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却是更原始的手段 战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今是唯一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.84,0:06:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时是单一文明圈的圣者 不喜好战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.48,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而对手的人类却因为过于愚昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持续拒绝战斗以外的接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马修的意志决定了制造战斗用机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是不被赋予战争以外之目的的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.51,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马修还让我们保留了圣者的心呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能不被毁灭 平安归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是要追求圣物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就非得舍弃掉世俗的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神圣和世俗宛如双胞胎兄弟般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一方成长的背后 必有另一方的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边留恋人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边又不使自己产生留恋之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的题目 不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来到你身边我可是第一次学习到这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们作为战士而诞生的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人类世界生活会有多困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有为了某些目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而把存在于心中的某些东西舍弃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是无可救药的留恋才能办到的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.25,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你为美里优鞠躬尽瘁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.32,0:08:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是为了向他及他的父亲赎罪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起初我是这么打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在却不只是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有阿优在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他朋友跟式条老师在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.11,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够像人类一样地过日子 我觉得非常的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以美里家女佣的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以安藤麻幌的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后我也想继续过着现在的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了这点 而不是为了谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V1046R—MAH0R0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太白星最强的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赌上了自己的存在 而决定走上的这条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我实在很难理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为战士的我能够理解你所选择的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很明显的 这是一场非打不可的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 就来决个胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的刀尖太重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃不了妄念吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有把起雾的镜子擦干净就来这里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的镜子才没有起雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去吧 你这个俗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人不耐烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.36,0:11:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠开枪 怎么可能打倒得了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何一直逃 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 你这样也称得上是战士吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然会在地板上睡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个完美无暇的美貌才是我的终极之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持充足睡眠才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道睡着了没？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉的样子也好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个洗衣板女佣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(给阿优)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为事发突然 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.83,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因为某些缘故 必须到远方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间虽然短暂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但与阿优相处的这段时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你至今的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没有发现呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说要去决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹用完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边好像也用得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来孤注一掷 赌输赢的时候似乎到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌到底去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点告诉我呀 史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我答应麻幌 不能告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.72,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你去也帮不上忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗用机械人的战争中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类去了也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确 或许我什么都帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最初来到这个家的时候曾对我说过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.49,0:16:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻幌的主人对你而言也是你的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这句话不是骗人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以主人的身份命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你带我去麻幌那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K 我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(接待大厅)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这些骗小孩的把戏有用吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何明知打不中还要使出这种武器呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言 为了赢得胜利的唯一策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要如何才能让这一击能够更正确的命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停电？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一百公里范围之内发生了反物质现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三秒后消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是麻幌所赌上的最后一击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.62,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果出现吉数的话 我和主人等于是白跑了这一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.73,0:20:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待续

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.39,0:23:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说人类好像相当怕死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.62,0:23:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是有百万年的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论是哪里的 谁都不知道自己何时会停止机能运作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.36,0:23:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有像这样在聊天时的瞬间 听得到的瞬间才是人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.03,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是如此吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.20,0:24:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正我的说教也不可能是什么良药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.11,0:24:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜每天的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.38,0:24:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可无法保证下次还能再跟你见到面喔
